   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(lines 10-19) The 28th year of Aurelius Commodus Antoninus Caesar the Lord, Mecheir 28. Paid to Nemesianus and Kallinikos, collectors-designate of the money-taxes of the metropolis � by Morion son of Apollonios � for the embankments-tax of the 27th year 7 drachmas 1/2 obol, for poll-tax of the 28th year 8 drachmas, for pig-tax 1 drachma 4 obols, for prison-guards-tax 1 obol, total 16 drachmas 5 1/2 obols. (4th hand) I, Nemesianos, have signed. (5th hand) I, Kallinikos, have signed.</ab>
